        <div id="faq" class="mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-orbitron font-bold text-primary mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 p-6 rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2">What is automated lead generation tools?</h3>
              <p class="text-white">Automated lead generation tools are software platforms that use AI and machine learning to identify, qualify, and engage potential customers automatically, reducing manual prospecting effort while improving lead quality and conversion rates.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 p-6 rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2">How much can automated lead generation tools improve sales performance?</h3>
              <p class="text-white">Organizations typically see 40-60% increases in qualified leads, 25-35% improvements in conversion rates, and 50-70% reduction in cost per acquisition when implementing comprehensive automated lead generation systems.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 p-6 rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2">What ROI can I expect from automated lead generation tools?</h3>
              <p class="text-white">Most companies achieve 300-500% ROI within 6-12 months through increased lead volume, improved quality, reduced manual effort, and faster sales cycles enabled by automation.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/30 p-6 rounded-xl">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-primary mb-2">How do automated lead generation tools ensure compliance with data privacy regulations?</h3>
              <p class="text-white">Modern platforms include built-in compliance features for GDPR, CCPA, and CAN-SPAM, including consent management, opt-out handling, data retention controls, and audit trails for regulatory reporting.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

